Field 
 public Field(int someAccessFlags,
              int aNameIndex,
              int aDescriptorIndex)
Build a Field. Note that this constructor cannot be used to create a field with attributes. Before calling this routine, you must either locate or create constants within the Constant Pool.

Parameters:
someAccessFlags - access flags (such as ACC_STATIC, etc.)
aNameIndex - the index of a ConstantUtf8 that names the field.
aDescriptorIndex - the index of a ConstantUtf8 that describes the field's type
